These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, horror, spy, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, disco, hip-hop, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, french, nigerian, australian
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, van, quad-bike
1. the french is the fan of punk##1
2. the nigerian is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching zombie movies##2
3. the french is the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the fan of folk is on the left of the egyptian##1
6. the person driving the van is the person watching spy movies##1
7. the fan of disco is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
8. the egyptian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | zombie   | romance  | spy  |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | punk    | folk      | hip-hop    |
| Nationality   | australian | french | nigerian | egyptian |
| Transport     | quad-bike  | car       | helicopter    | van     |

