.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, board-games, chess, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, horror, satire
4 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, goldfish, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, parkour, snowboarding, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the turtle is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person watching satire movies is between the owner of the goldfish and the person who's sport is surfing##2
6. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person watching satire movies and the owner of the turtle##2
7. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | board-games    | chess  | traveling    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime      | drama  | satire  | horror |
| Pet           | turtle      | goldfish       | hedgehog      | mouse       |
| Sport         | parkour    | rowing | snowboarding | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, pepper, eggplant, orange
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, board-games, gardening, baking
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, architect, security-guard
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, van, tram, trike
1. the architect is the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the security-guard##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the librarian is the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person eating orange is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the person eating apricot is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is baking##2
9. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person eating eggplant and the librarian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | pepper | eggplant     | apricot   | orange     |
| Hobby       | board-games   | dancing   | gardening | baking |
| Job         | designer   | architect | security-guard       | librarian    |
| Transport   | tram    | van | boat  | trike    |

