.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, nurse, manager, architect
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, horror, zombie, western
4 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, rat, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, basketball, cricket, golf
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching western movies is the freelancer##1
 3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching western movies is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is the manager##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the nurse is between the owner of the snake and the architect##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | freelancer  | architect | nurse     | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | western | thriller  | zombie | horror       |
| Pet           | guinea-pig       | turtle    | rat      | snake           |
| Sport         | tennis | basketball   | golf   | cricket         |

