.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, avocado, watermelon, lettuce
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, designer, coach, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, disaster, mystery, superhero
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, skateboarding, biathlon, golf
 1. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
 3. the coach is the person eating avocado##1
 4. the coach is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the writer is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 8. the designer is the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the person eating watermelon is between the person who's sport is golf and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
10. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | avocado         | watermelon         | lime     | lettuce      |
| Job           | coach | writer | police-officer    | designer     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts      | mystery       | superhero    | disaster       |
| Sport         | swimming     | biathlon       | golf | skateboarding |

