.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, scientist, electrician, designer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, soul, dubstep
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, colombian, french, american
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, skateboarding, handball
1. the fan of ambient is between the person who's sport is handball and the fan of soul##2
2. the scientist is between the fan of ambient and the american##2
3. the french is between the person who's sport is rowing and the colombian##2
4. the electrician is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the french is the french##1
6. the colombian is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
7. the colombian is on the left of the lawyer##1
8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
9. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | scientist | lawyer  | designer |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | dubstep       | ambient     | soul      |
| Nationality   | american   | colombian      | french   | nigerian   |
| Sport         | skateboarding   | handball    | basketball | rowing   |

