 5. the japanese is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the australian is the person driving the ship##1
 8. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
10. the spanish is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
