3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the bike and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
6. the person drinking milk is the person watching spy movies##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
