.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, pumpkin, cabbage, orange
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, lawyer, analyst, architect
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, salsa, hip-hop, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, baseball, snowboarding, ice-hockey
 1. the person eating pumpkin is the analyst##1
 2. the person eating orange is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the analyst is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 5. the fan of punk is the person eating plum##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
 7. the lawyer is on the left of the analyst##1
 8. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
 9. the dressmaker is between the architect and the person who's sport is golf##2
10. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | orange        | cabbage    | plum | pumpkin   |
| Job           | architect | dressmaker | lawyer   | analyst |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop         | techno       | punk      | salsa     |
| Sport         | snowboarding       | ice-hockey | golf    | baseball  |

