.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, soy-milk, 7up
There 4 different types of food: papaya, pomegranate, apple, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, fishing, singing, drawing
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit, lizard, mouse
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person eating papaya is the person drinking tea##1
 5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is between the person eating papaya and the person eating apple##2
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person eating papaya and the person eating apple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | tea    | soy-milk    | 7up      | coffee |
| Food       | papaya        | cauliflower       | apple       | pomegranate     |
| Hobby      | singing | gardening | drawing | fishing        |
| Pet        | rabbit       | mouse     | lizard         | ferret           |

