 3. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 5. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the snake##2
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating lime##1
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the snake is the person driving the bike##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
